Usage: write_ml_timing_graph [-help] [-noedge] -prefix <string>
                             [-register_only] [-views <view_list>]

-help                # Prints out the command usage
-noedge              # Don't dump edge, for time saving (bool, optional)
-prefix <string>     # Prefix for output files (string, required)
-register_only       # Only dump nodes for register (bool, optional)
-views <view_list>   # Dump data for the specified analysis view(s).
                     # (tcl_obj, optional)